      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Two more electrical contractors\nsigned up with the union this\nmorning. They are the North Side\nElectric Co. and the Western Elec-\ntrio Co. Practically all the union\nelectrical workers that have been\nlocked out in the other shops about\ntown are now employed II is said\n. more journeymen are wanted but\ncannot be found.\n\n\nThe contractors did not declare\nan open shop at noon today, as\nthreatened Saturday in case the\nelectrical workers did ont agree to\ntheir terms, Instead, another meet\nIng has been called in the Spo-\nkane Electric Co.'S shop this after\nnoon."
    }
